{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Blob()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob/Blob","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/File_API\">File API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><em><code>Blob()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob/size\"><code>size</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob/type\"><code>type</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob/arrayBuffer\"><code>arrayBuffer()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob/slice\"><code>slice()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob/stream\"><code>stream()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob/text\"><code>text()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>File API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileList\"><code>FileList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReaderSync\"><code>FileReaderSync</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURL\"><code>URL.createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>URL.revokeObjectURL()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><code><strong>Blob()</strong></code> コンストラクターは、新たな <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> オブジェクトを返します。その blob の中身は、引数 <code>array</code> で与えられた値を連結したものから構成されています。</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <var>newBlob</var> = new Blob(<var>array</var>, <var>options</var>);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"array\"><code><var>array</var></code></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array\"><code>Array</code></a> で、その中身が <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray\"><code>ArrayBufferView</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a> のオブジェクト、またはそのようなオブジェクトの何れかが混合したもので、それが <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> の中に入れられます。 <code>USVString</code> オブジェクトは UTF-8 で符号化されたものです。</dd>\n <dt id=\"options\"><code><var>options</var></code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">省略可</span></dt>\n <dd>\n <p>任意で、以下のプロパティを指定する <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>BlobPropertyBag</code></a> オブジェクトです。</p>\n\n <dl>\n  <dt id=\"type\"><code>type</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">省略可</span></dt>\n  <dd>blob に格納されるデータの <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/MIME_type\">MIME タイプ</a> です。既定値は空文字列 (<code>\"\"</code>) です。</dd>\n  <dt id=\"endings\"><code>endings</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">省略可</span> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>データがテキストの場合、コンテンツ内の改行文字 (<code>\\n</code>) の解釈方法を示します。既定値は <code>transparent</code> であり、改行文字を変換することなく blob に格納します。改行文字をホストシステムの慣行に合わせるには、<code>endings</code> を指定してください。</dd>\n </dl>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>指定されたデータを含む <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> オブジェクトです。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js  language-js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> aFileParts <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'&lt;a id=\"a\"&gt;&lt;b id=\"b\"&gt;hey!&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 単一の DOMString からなる配列</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> oMyBlob <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Blob</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>aFileParts<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token literal-property property\">type</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'text/html'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// blob</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/FileAPI/#constructorBlob\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">File API<br><small lang=\"ja\">Blob() の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td>初回定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Blob.Blob","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob/Blob/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"あわせて参照","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>このコンストラクターによって置き換えられた非推奨の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BlobBuilder\"><code>BlobBuilder</code></a> インターフェイス</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specification"},{"text":"ブラウザの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"あわせて参照","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Blob() コンストラクターは、新たな Blob オブジェクトを返します。その blob の中身は、引数 array で与えられた値を連結したものから構成されています。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Blob()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Blob()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Blob()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Blob()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Blob","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Blob()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Blob()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Blob()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/blob/blob","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/blob/blob/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob","title":"Blob"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob/Blob","title":"Blob()"}],"pageTitle":"Blob() - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}